ent()\n    # Does NOT count toward usage limit\n    # Allows indefinite conversations"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Conditions"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- ✅ Code execution must be enabled\n- ✅ Paid Claude plan (Pro, Max, Team, Enterprise)\n- ❌ Edge cases: Very large first messages or system errors may still hit limits"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[support.claude](https://support.claude.com/en/articles/8606394-how-large-is-the-context-window-on-paid-claude-plans)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Model-Specific Details"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Opus 4.5 (Enterprise)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Standard context: 200K tokens\nExtended context: Up to 1M tokens (enterprise deployment)\n\nOutput limit: 64,000 tokens per response\nRecommended for production: 20K–80K tokens per request"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude 3.5 Sonnet (Legacy)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Context window: 200,000 tokens (increased from 100K in Oct 2024)\nOutput limit: 8,192 tokens (beta) or 4,096 tokens (default)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Historical"},{"type":"text","text":": Claude 3.5 Sonnet's 200K window was "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"double"},{"type":"text","text":" the previous 100K limit when released in October 2024"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Quick Reference: Key Limits"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text